:1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T06:59:59.000Z","msg":"議會無左咪諗集體走囉，天無絕人之路<br />\n<br />\n成日叫對手咩手下留情，中國人社會不嬲都係有風駛盡𢃇，幾廿歲人發完夢未<br />\n<br />\n真係唔知嘅，去睇下Stanford prison experiment係咩黎啦，本身無後果，有權唔用盡本身就違反人性<br />\n<br />\n好心呢班係香港搞民主嘅面對現實啦<br />\n<br />\n反正今日香港留係度得個殼黎都係嘥氣<br />\n<br />\n上一代層樓全部高價，全部肯套現集體走人都仲未遲<br />\n<br />\n好過無啦啦出去比人屈坐政治獄，製造更多悲劇"},{"pid":"1befd25e14f4a59b696d01ec1ac0d15bb60950a6","tid":496554,"uid":34103,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T07:03:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b77dda8e3a6e72ee0a34fd6dc6930eace24aaf0","tid":496554,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T07:04:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a5d5e8d9ddd0a18b44253288a26cb7b14dcec15","tid":496554,"uid":47359,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T07:05:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁凍真係不了<br />\n反正去左都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛dewi</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/150507_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F150507_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3c48cad1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e6fc5e8a064b1744e5a51e42f10f265b6541a82","tid":496554,"uid":44358,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T07:05:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>勁撚多五盾狗幫保皇狗轉移視線</blockquote><br />\n五毛block極都仲有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五毛數量好似比以前高登更多，好多都陰陰濕濕，散佈失敗主義叫人放棄做順民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b610cd46ae51d3b8963f089f1cefc254bf82e1","tid":496554,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T07:06:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"abcdf8b6ef7b0d86217e0b14b5fe863fa90cf1cd","tid":496554,"uid":106026,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T07:15:25.000Z","msg":"衝既時候,你地話人係鬼.<br />\n叫你地唔好含撚投票,你地聽哂雷動計劃話.<br />\n當有六個議員被DQ,叫你地總辭,你地話個啲人係鬼.<br />\n叫你地唔好大和解,你地就話唔好搞分化.<br />\n<br />\nok fine,俾哂你地搞,結果搞到咁,你地就話點解無人出黎,點守得住議會.真係光環就你地攞,有咩失敗就賴其他人,食屎啦,我係屋企瞓覺都唔會出黎,廢事又俾你地話係鬼."},{"pid":"6eb4142a5ccdfb953686dd8a1702adbebb977773","tid":496554,"uid":74214,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:01:42.000Z","msg":"lihkg熱門無一個post同議事規則有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"702ee2f1a5ee450e9e15119947a32a0dc508d95e","tid":496554,"uid":60959,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:03:56.000Z","msg":"劇本已經寫好<br />\n<br />\n1.大叫可恥當升左級<br />\n2.係電視機下比人抬出會議廳<br />\n3.修改議事規則最後通過<br />\n4.民主派開記招，流曬馬尿話今日係民主最黑暗一日，然後話日後仲有好多場仗要打，搬曬d高鐵，23條出來<br />\n5.記招最後就會話會繼續監察政府<br />\n6.動員社運KOL,黃絲，大中華膠去幫飯民去污名化 (例如黎則奮，細黃伯，區家麟)，內容不外乎懶感性中二病文章，例子有&rdquo;.....殊死決戰&rdquo;，&rdquo;時代選中我們走在一起&rdquo;<br />\n7.和理非香港人一呼百應，感謝佢地既付出，邊個唔認同就會批鬥佢地，理由不外乎&rdquo;獨立呀&rdquo;，&rdquo;勇武呀&rdquo;，&rdquo;從政一定要知所進退&rdquo;<br />\n8.如常繼續返工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dcfc851fcb3240a2fa3dd48ffc38134a9110fb2","tid":496554,"uid":60959,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:04:36.000Z","msg":"議會幾時有過抗爭空間呀？我地活響平行世界架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97658e1f4bf4ac769817f0a234aaac4b8fba60a8","tid":496554,"uid":74214,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:09:54.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 點解咁撚多五毛㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f475951ce32e6cfdc39e882a42fdc93732cd8d1","tid":496554,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:10:40.000Z","msg":"港豬: 點抗爭啊， 唔使返工咩, 搞到坐監點算, <br />\n所以中共根本唔驚香港人, 因為香港惡唔出樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfbc75c876b3144d3e4c4d2af4dba889597941e7","tid":496554,"uid":74214,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:11:33.000Z","msg":"講返工不了個啲人真係好撚戇鳩，以為講完有人工加<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0706cd2f41300796aba1bc19b7f6b9e2cde5e3b7","tid":496554,"uid":56157,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:12:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>lihkg熱門無一個post同議事規則有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為你應該問返到底改唔改有乜用?<br />\n無23條仲有不誠實使用電腦(萬能key)<br />\n各種基建搶錢泛民停唔到。<br />\n<br />\n最重要係，今時今日作為泛民既，資歷最老，<br />\n然後作為當日最關鍵推今時今日大口狗上去既梁耀忠先生仲未引咎辭職<br />\n泛民又無左關鍵一席。<br />\n<br />\n由DQ事件開始，明眼人一早就知議會廢撚左十世。<br />\n林鄭當日都夠薑講，高鐵啟動三步走唔需要理你立法會過唔過無約束力議案。"},{"pid":"3f7ffb83d2350b7fbd118a6553b040bd578c79a1","tid":496554,"uid":60959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:13:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講返工不了個啲人真係好撚戇鳩，以為講完有人工加<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你琴晚有冇落去佔領呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"e7ce26a3a0fecd31de9a7fbf86372cca4f352bac","tid":496554,"uid":67485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:14:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19843a87a93e781f3e617b7f82fd485f7dc9c0c7","tid":496554,"uid":56157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:14:42.000Z","msg":"老實講要開聲既時機一早過左，早係DQ事件泛民就要出聲嘈。<br />\n而唔係配合政府玩補選。<br />\n泛民放棄其他做法陪政府玩（總辭又好其他野都好）<br />\n咁佢今日使橫手，仲有咩好出聲?"},{"pid":"add79d0c44efa01dab314d0861eebd8050f47a27","tid":496554,"uid":60959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:15:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>劇本已經寫好<br />\n<br />\n1.大叫可恥當升左級<br />\n2.係電視機下比人抬出會議廳<br />\n3.修改議事規則最後通過<br />\n4.民主派開記招，流曬馬